a real tennis court and face professional tennis players. \nYou'll have to show all your technical and tactical skills.\n\nVR Controls:\nHold the controller/racket and play tennis.\n\nFeatures: \n- Arcade and Simulation mode.\n- Online Multiplayer.\n- 3 different ways to run through the court: Teleport, Run in Place, Sliding Run.\n- One handed serve.\n- 7 different court surfaces: clay, grass, hard, blue-green hard, classic synthetic, indoor hard and indoor synthetic; each with a specific rebound. \n- 13 tournaments: 4 Slam and 9 Masters. \n- Full ranking system. \n- Fully customizable 3D male player. ", "short_description": "First Person Tennis is the first tennis simulator developed for VR. Now, you can play on a real tennis court and face professional tennis players. You'll have to show all your technical and tactical skills."}]}, "developer_name": "Mikori Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/fptprivacypolicy/home-page", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.facebook.com/MikoriGames/", "publisher_name": "Mikori Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.facebook.com/Firstpersontennis", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SPORTS", "SIMULATION", "ACTION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["de", "ru", "en", "pt_BR", "it", "fr", "es", "ja", "zh_CN"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "3168313566780415"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 37, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1187353675903654"}, {"status": "PUBLISHE